content:
Compose MCP servers into: {{composed_name}}

Servers to Compose:
{{#each servers}}
- {{this.name}} (prefix: {{this.prefix}})
{{/each}}

Additional Tools:
{{#each additional_tools}}
- {{this.name}}: {{this.description}}
{{/each}}

Composition Implementation:
```python
#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""{{composed_name}} - Composed MCP Server."""
from sparetools.mcp_core.server.composer import ServerComposer

{{#each servers}}
from {{this.module}} import {{this.app_name}}
{{/each}}

# Create composer
composer = ServerComposer("{{composed_name}}")

# Add servers
{{#each servers}}
composer.add_server({{this.app_name}}, prefix="{{this.prefix}}")
{{/each}}

# Add additional tools
{{#each additional_tools}}
composer.add_tool(
    "{{this.name}}",
    {{this.handler}},
    description="{{this.description}}"
)
{{/each}}

# Export composed app
app = composer.get_server()

if __name__ == "__main__":
    composer.run()
```

MCP Configuration:
```json
{
  "{{composed_name}}": {
    "command": "{{command}}",
    "args": {{args}},
    "env": {{env}}
  }
}
```
